						<td class="table-cols table-cols-desc align-middle text-center">Equipment collected during the Bonus Stage after killing Elite Bosses fall into this category.</td>
						<td class="table-cols table-cols-desc align-middle text-center">Most unique equipment dropped directly by bosses and equipment crafted by shards/materials obtained from these bosses are considered "Boss" items. There are also certain special items not obtainable through bosses that belong to this category.</td>
